description:
First produced for [Greenpeace's London HQ](https://www.opendesk.cc/workspaces/greenpeace), the Fin Bookshelf is part of the growing Fin range. The Bookshelf and its sibling, the Lockers, imagineer storage solutions for the design conscious. 

The Bookshelf features multiple depths, casting new contrasts and facilitates smarter organisation. With the traditional no-metal-parts Opendesk approach the Bookshelf is assembled seamlessly with every part carefully considered and highly material efficient. Designed to be standalone or joined, the Fin range slots in numerous workspace configurations with minimum fuss.
name: Fin Bookshelf
